title: Darkest Dungeon Build 11931
description:
Title: Darkest Dungeon
Genre: Indie, RPG, Strategy, Early Access
Developer: Red Hook Studios 
Publisher: Red Hook Studios+
Build: 11931	
Release Date: 3 Feb, 2015

Hotfix Build #11931
Overall goal of this hotfix is to reduce stress in Apprentice level quests. (Also reduces some overall deadliness.) 

Reduced crit on Brigand Bloodletter, Brigand Fusilier, and Bone Courtier 
Reduced Brigand Fusilier debuff 
Reduced Cultist Witch's target AI for Apprentice quests 
Reduced crits from Apprentice level monsters 
Made Collector's "Show Collection" stress more consistent 
Abomination now acts as intended when controlled by Siren

Install & Play
